%% Mermaid architecture diagram for FA Sanity Check
flowchart LR
  PO[Purchase Order] --> GRN[Goods Received Note]
  GRN -->|create stock_moves receipt| StockMovesIn[stock_moves (inbound)]
  StockMovesIn -->|FIFO assign| Sales[Sales Invoice / Delivery]
  Sales --> StockMovesOut[stock_moves (outbound)]
  StockMovesOut --> FIFO[ItemTrace FIFO allocation]
  Sales -->|creates debtor_trans / payments| Payments[Payments]
  Payments -->|bank_trans| BankTrans[bank_trans]
  BankTrans -->|processor or direct| Processor[Processor Accounts]
  Processor -->|settlement| FinalCash[Final Cash Accounts]
  FinalCash -->|deposit| BankTrans

  classDef db fill:#f9f,stroke:#333,stroke-width:1px
  class StockMovesIn,StockMovesOut,BankTrans db
